 |archivedate = 2008-01-19
}} (Free registration required for online access)</ref>。磷脂酰丝氨酸在正常情况下仅存在于质膜靠[[细胞质|细胞质]]一侧的表面上，但在细胞凋亡時，磷脂酰丝氨酸会由「{{Link-en|磷脂促翻转酶|Scramblase}}」（scramblase）移到到质膜的外侧（磷脂促翻转酶目前還未發現，只是一種假說中的蛋白）<ref name="phago2">{{Cite journal |title=Cell corpse engulfment mediated by ''C. elegans'' phosphatidylserine receptor through CED-5 and CED-12 |author=Wang X |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/302/5650/1563 |journal=Science |issue=5650 |doi=10.1126/science.1087641 |year=2003 |volume=302 |pages=1563–1566 |pmid=14645848 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080521032606/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/302/5650/1563 |archivedate=2008-05-21 |deadurl=no |access-date=2016-06-17 }} (Free registration required for online access)</ref>。細胞表面的磷脂酰丝氨酸為該細胞進行了標記，使巨噬细胞上相应的受体能夠加以辨識，並將該细胞吞噬<ref name="phago1">{{Cite journal |title=Eat me or die |journal=Science |issue=5650 |doi=10.1126/science.1092533 |year=2003 |volume=302 |pages=1516–17 |pmid=14645835 |vauthors=Savill J, Gregory C, Haslett C}}</ref>。透過吞噬细胞清理凋亡細胞的過程經過妥善安排，不会引发[[炎症反应|炎症反应]]，這也是吞噬细胞的一項重要功能<ref name="pmid18774293">{{cite journal
